    "description": "<p>St. Andrew's Mission Hospital (SAMH) first began as a free dispensary for poor local and migrant women and children in&nbsp;1913. &nbsp;Today, SAMH operates St. Andrew's Community Hospital, St. Andrew’s Autism Centre, St. Andrew’s Mission Hospital Clinics, St. Andrew’s Nursing Homes at Buangkok, Henderson and Queenstown and St. Andrew’s Senior Care centres at Kampong Glam, Tampines, Henderson and Queenstown.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>St. John's-St. Margaret’s Nursing Home and Senior Care Centre at Dover Avenue will begin operations in 2021.</p>",
